In the same vein, It would be nice if there were an option to indent after a hubl loop or if statement.
Example, this:
```{% if module.paste %}
    &lt;some stuff&gt;&lt;/some stuff&gt;
{% endif %}```

Instead of this:
```{% if module.paste %}
&lt;some stuff&gt;&lt;/some stuff&gt;
{% endif %}```
